logic: all events of acute pancreatitis, indexed on an inpatient or emergency or an out patient visit (restricted to overlapping with an Emergency room procedures) with a diagnosis of Acute pancreatitis. With  1. no such events in prior washout window of 365 days 2. and no history of chronic pancreatitis any time prior or hereditary  pancreatitis any time pre or post index. Cohort exit is 7 days post index.
